# Shigayevo, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Shigayevo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kabansky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 513 as of 2010. There are 5 streets.
Geography
Shigayevo is located 21&nbsp;km northwest of Kabansk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Murzino is the nearest rural locality.
